  "description": "Symbolize your eternal love with this elegant wave-inspired Moissanite wedding ring. Crafted from premium S925 sterling silver with a refined white gold finish, this ring features five dazzling D-color VVS1 Moissanite stones, totaling 0.07 carats. The center stone is slightly larger, flanked on each side by two smaller stones, creating a balanced and graceful design that represents enduring love and harmony.\n\nThe inner band is engraved with “S925” and “0.07CT,” marking the ring's quality and gemstone weight, ensuring you’re wearing a piece of elegance and authenticity.\n\nKey Features:\n\nWave Eternity Design: A sophisticated symbol of everlasting love and unity.\n\nPremium Moissanite Stones: D-color, VVS1 clarity stones with a total weight of 0.07 carats, arranged to maximize brilliance.\n\nS925 Sterling Silver: Hypoallergenic, durable, and beautifully finished in white gold.\n\nAuthenticity Markings: \"S925\" and \"0.07CT\" engraved for assurance of quality and value.\n\nCelebrate a lifetime of commitment with a ring as beautiful and enduring as your love.\n\nMaterial: 925 Sterling Silver\n\nCarat Weight: 0.07ct\n\nColor Grade : D\n\nClarity Grade: VVS1\n\nCut Grade: Excellent",
